<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM4.5.9">
<l>vāyo rupakkam vāṅkiva lippa</l>
<l rend="indent">vārnta nīrkkuḻik kaṇkaḷmi ḻaṟṟa</l>
<l>tāyo rupakkan tantaiyoru pakkan</l>
<l rend="indent">tāra mumoru pakkama laṟṟa</l>
<l>tīyō rupakkañ cērvataṉ muṉṉañ</l>
<l rend="indent">ceṅkaṇ māloṭuñ cikkaṉac cuṟṟa</l>
<l>māyo rupakkan niṟkaval lārkku</l>
<l rend="indent">ara vataṇṭat tiluyyalu māmē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>While prattling on,</l>
<l rend="indent">pain throbing on one side of the mouth,</l>
<l rend="indent">mucous increasing,</l>
<l rend="indent">[and] eyes hollowed out,</l>
<l>[your] mother on one side, father on one side,</l>
<l rend="indent">[your] wife babbling incessently on another side –</l>
<l>before the fire reaches the [last] side,</l>
<l>[take note that] for those who are able to remain on one side as relatives</l>
<l rend="indent">who have entanglements with red-eyed Māl,</l>
<l>they will escape the punishment of Yama.</l>

      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
